When you play an Attack card, if you have Feral, consume 1 stack to deal damage 1 additional time.
通感 Synesthesia ：打出本牌时，每个分身都额外打出一次本牌。
When this card is played, each Duplicate plays this card 1 additional time.
咏唱 Chant ：见希赛莉的卡表描述。
